Day 58: Deploy Grafana on Kubernetes Cluster

Date: October 24, 2025
Overview
Deployed Grafana for monitoring and visualization.
Key Concepts Learned

Monitoring stack deployment
Persistent volumes for stateful apps
Service configuration
Dashboard persistence

Commands Used
bashkubectl create deployment grafana --image=grafana/grafana
kubectl expose deployment grafana --type=NodePort --port=3000
kubectl create pvc grafana-storage
Challenges Faced
Data persistence! Grafana needed PersistentVolumeClaims to retain dashboards.
